ng sound. Finally a silent mattress protector!Silent! That was the biggest concern that I had when I was getting a mattress protector; How noisy is this going to be. So many other reviews say they are noisy when sleeping on them. I have not been able to hear a thing! We have the thinner summer sheets on due to the heat. I rolled around and moved all over the bed to see how much noise it would make. I didn't hear a thing! I also dumped a cup of water on the protector to see if the mattress protector would hold up. To my satisfaction the mattress was completely dry. I have been completely satisfied with this mattress protector. I would recommend it to everyone!much nicer than plastic coversI received this mattress protector for free to try it out.  I was very pleased to find that the fabric and feel of this waterproof cover is so comfortable and durable.  I have used many vinyl mattress protectors over the years that tear easily and are noisy and uncomfortable to use.  This protector is soft, quiet, durable and comfortable.I hope to get these for all my mattress's.  
This is the perfect mattress protector.  I love that it is waterproof, but not noisy like other waterproof mattresses.  It is soft and comfortable and really great on my new 16" memory foam gel mattress.  It was exactly what I was looking for to protect the mattress without changing the feel of the mattress. It doesn't add bulk just protection.  Excellent mattress protectorThis mattres protector is actually breathable and cool. I used it for the first time and did not get too warm at all. My mattress top is bamboo, and is extremely soft. With this protector it is a little less soft because of the waterproof material. However, I don't think you can get away from that with a mattress protector of you want it to be water proof. This is an excellent choice! The last one I bought must have been polyester because it was so hot to sleep on. I love this one! Highly recommend.Like your favorite t-shirt, but for your bedI was sent this mattress cover to give it an honest review. A lot of mattress protectors are very “plastic-y,” but this one is very soft and stretchy—like your favorite t-shirt, but for your bed. It really is water-proof--we poured a little water on the mattress after we put the protector on, and the mattress stayed dry. The nice, thick zipper was super easy to maneuver. This mattress protector is very well constructed, and I do not doubt it could last years and years. It took us a while to figure out the easiest way to slip the protector on the bed, but all was well after a few attempts. Great ProductMy daughter peed in her twin bed this morning and not a single drop touched the matress. I will be buying another one from being so satisfied with this item. It's a real life saver.Excellent protectorThis is a excellent Matress protector and is very soft, however it does not cool like I would like. I still wake up sweating :-(Matress protection.Haven't needed it to protect matress yet but know its there.Sponsored LinksWhat's This?SizesQueenTwinKingFullSuper Singl