Shopping Tips & Inspiration







How to Protect Your Home from the Bed Bug Epidemic

How to Protect Your Home from the Bed Bug Epidemic from Overstock.com. Our guides provide customers with information about protecting your home.







Bedding Buying Guide

The look and feel of your bed are determined by several different pieces of bedding. Use our bedding tips to help you choose the best bedding for your bed and help every item work together to create a bed you'll love falling into every night.








How to Pick Memory Foam Mattress Topper Thickness

A memory foam mattress topper can transform the feel of your bed, improving your sleep experience. Choosing the right topper thickness will keep you cradled and comfortable all night long. Use these suggestions to narrow down your options.







Best Bedding for Christmas

Update your home and keep everyone on your shopping list warm and bundled up this Christmas with our best bedding gift ideas. Shop our huge selection of bedding at Overstock.com.







ComforPedic from Beautyrest Memory Foam Buying Guide

ComforPedic&trade; from Beautyrest&trade;, a global memory foam technology leader, has developed technological advances designed to overcome the feeling of sinking or the hard-to-move sensations associated with other memory foams.







Tencel Bedding Buying Guide

Learn all you need to know about TENCEL&reg;: what it is, where it comes from, and what makes it the perfect fit for your bedding needs.







How to Choose a Mattress Pad

How to Choose a Mattress Pad from Overstock.com. Mattress pads can do so much for your bed. When you know what you want one to do for your bed, buying one will be simple.







Welcoming Guest Room Ideas

An inviting guest bedroom adds to a guest's experience, whether they're on vacation or just passing through. Welcome visitors with their very own home away from home.







Sheets Buying Guide

Bed sheets made from different materials feel different, look different, and have unique benefits. Some sheets provide plenty of warmth during cold nights, and others are light and breathable for summer sleeping. Use this guide to learn everything you need to know before choosing which bed sheets to slip into every night.







3 Quick Tips for Better Sleep

When we get quality sleep, we have more energy to function our best in our day-to-day lives. But if you’re like me, sometimes it’s a struggle to get the kind of rest you need. These quick tips have helped me enjoy deeper, better sleep, which means I wake up refreshed and ready to go.







Brighter Bedrooms

Bring some color to your dreams with a bedroom makeover.

















