“Terry has transformed our house, he is easy to get along with and is happy to explain his work. He completed a new damp proof course filled in many cracks and applied the coating among other things. The finish is incredible and we are finally house proud again. I would not hesitate in recommending him to anyone and would use him again in the future.”Callum S, Maidstone, Kent
 
“The exterior of our offices is looking superb, Terry.  Thanks again for your extremely hard work on the preparation and repairs. The finished effect is stunning!”Joe V,​ Croydon, Surrey
